bilingual.target: 这个投资者的业务量非常多样化。

bilingual.source: An investor needs to carefully study market trends.
bilingual.target: 投资者需要仔细研究市场趋势。

bilingual.source: The grabby investor bought up all the shares.
bilingual.target: 那个贪婪的投资者买下了所有的股票。

bilingual.source: The investor is bullish about the stock market this year.
bilingual.target: 投资者对今年的股市看涨。

bilingual.source: The project is backed by a well-known investor.
bilingual.target: 这个项目得到了一个知名投资者的支持。

bilingual.source: The investor attended the annual shareholders' meeting.
bilingual.target: 这位投资者参加了年度股东大会。

bilingual.source: An astute investor can often predict market trends.
bilingual.target: 一个精明的投资者常常能预测市场趋势。

bilingual.source: As an investor, you must understand risk management.
bilingual.target: 作为一名投资者，你必须了解风险管理。

bilingual.source: The investor waited for a propitious moment to buy stocks.
bilingual.target: 投资者等待一个顺利的时机购买股票。

bilingual.source: An experienced investor knows how to diversify investments.
bilingual.target: 经验丰富的投资者知道如何分散投资。

list.abstract: investor是一个英语单词，可以用作名词，可以翻译为投资者、出资者，等等。

yingyinNormal.en: At least I was up. What do you have besides an idea? They've got an investor!
yingyinNormal.zh: 至少我涨过，你们除了点子之外还有啥？她们有投资者！

yingyinNormal.en: Great. Hey, John. Thank you for your vote of confidence. And welcome to the Investor's Center.
yingyinNormal.zh: 太好了，谢谢你的信任票，欢迎来到投资者中心。

yingyinNormal.en: But don't feel too bad for him. He's doing very well as a small business investor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但别为他感到难过，他现在做的小生意很有起色。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person or organization that puts money into financial schemes, or property with the expectation of achieving a profit

examination_example.sentence: Like other start-up <highlight>investors</highlight>, Mr. Arnold's own business often depends on selling start-ups to larger tech companies.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 像其他初创企业投资者一样，阿诺德自己的业务通常依赖于将初创企业出售给大型科技公司。

examination_example.sentence: Transient <highlight>investors</highlight>, who demand high quarterly profits from companies, can hinder a firm's efforts to invest in long-term research or to build up customer loyalty.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 要求从公司获得高额回报的短期投资者，会阻碍公司在长期研究和建立客户忠诚度的努力。

examination_example.sentence: When you remember such things you can automatically become <highlight>investor</highlight> in their wellbeing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你记住这些事情时，你就会自动成为他们幸福的投资者。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person or organization that puts money into financial schemes, or property with the expectation of achieving a profit

examination_example.sentence: But that won't stop inventors from dreaming up new ways to fly and trying to persuade <highlight>investors</highlight> to back their sometimes outrageous schemes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但这并不会阻止发明者想出新的飞行方式，并试图说服投资者支持他们有时离谱的计划。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Investors</highlight> shouldn't write off brick and mortar.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 投资者不应注销实体店。

examination_example.sentence: That won't stop inventors from dreaming up new ways to fly and trying to persuade <highlight>investors</highlight> to back their sometimes outrageous schemes.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这不会阻止发明家们追求新飞行方式的梦想，他们还试图说服投资者支持那些有时看起来很离谱的计划。

examination_example.sentence: But the boost in <highlight>investor</highlight> confidence needed for the plan to work will take time.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是，该计划实施所需的投资者信心的提升需要时间。
